[{"location":"api/#API","page":"API","title":"API","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"api/","page":"API","title":"API","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.PosteriorDB","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.PosteriorDB","text":"PosteriorDB\n\nFunctionality for working with instances of a posterior database.\n\nSee https://github.com/stan-dev/posteriordb for more information.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"module"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.AbstractImplementation","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.AbstractImplementation","text":"AbstractImplementation\n\nAbstract type for implementations of a model.\n\nSubtypes should implement the methods load and path.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.Dataset","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.Dataset","text":"Dataset\n\nPointer to a dataset in a PosteriorDatabase.\n\nSee also: dataset, dataset_names\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.Model","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.Model","text":"Model\n\nPointer to a model in a PosteriorDatabase.\n\nSee also: model, model_names\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.Posterior","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.Posterior","text":"Posterior\n\nPointer to a posterior in a PosteriorDatabase.\n\nSee also: posterior, posterior_names\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase","text":"PosteriorDatabase\n\nA posterior database object using the files at path.\n\nSee also: database, posterior_names, model_names, dataset_names\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.ReferencePosterior","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.ReferencePosterior","text":"ReferencePosterior\n\nPointer to a reference posterior in a PosteriorDatabase.\n\nSee also: Posterior, reference_posterior, posterior\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.StanModelImplementation","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.StanModelImplementation","text":"StanModelImplementation\n\nImplementation of a model using Stan.\n\nSee also: implementation, load\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.database","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.database","text":"database([path::String]) -> PosteriorDatabase\n\nReturn a pointer to the PosteriorDatabase stored at path.\n\nIf path is not given, the default posterior database downloaded from a GitHub release is used.\n\nnote: Note\nJulia 1.3 or greater is required to use the default posterior database with database().\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.database-Tuple{Any}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.database","text":"database(obj) -> PosteriorDatabase\n\nReturn the database containing obj.\n\nobj can be a Posterior, Model, AbstractImplementation, Dataset, or ReferencePosterior.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.dataset-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase, String}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.dataset","text":"dataset(db::PosteriorDatabase, name::String) -> Dataset\n\nReturn a dataset object for the dataset with name name in the database db.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.dataset-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Posterior}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.dataset","text":"dataset(posterior::Posterior) -> Dataset\n\nReturn the dataset entry of posterior.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.dataset_names-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.dataset_names","text":"dataset_names(db::PosteriorDatabase) -> Vector{String}\n\nReturn the names of all datasets in the database.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.implementation-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Model, String}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.implementation","text":"implementation(model::Model, framework::String) -> AbstractImplementation\n\nReturn the implementation of the model for the given framework.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.implementation_names-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Model}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.implementation_names","text":"implementation_names(model::Model) -> Vector{String}\n\nReturn the names of frameworks with code for the model.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.info-Tuple{Any}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.info","text":"info(obj) -> AbstractDict\n\nReturn the info dictionary for obj.\n\nobj can be a Posterior, Model, Dataset, or ReferencePosterior.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.load-Tuple{PosteriorDB.AbstractImplementation}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.load","text":"load(implementation::AbstractImplementation) -> String\n\nLoad the model implementation and return the code as a string.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.load-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Dataset}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.load","text":"load(dataset::Dataset) -> OrderedDict{String,Any}\n\nLoad and return the data for dataset.\n\nload(dataset::Dataset, String) -> String\n\nReturn the data for dataset as an unparsed JSON string.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.load-Tuple{PosteriorDB.ReferencePosterior}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.load","text":"load(rp::ReferencePosterior) -> Vector{OrderedDict{String,Any}}\n\nLoad and return the reference draws for the reference posterior rp.\n\nload(rp::ReferencePosterior, String) -> String\n\nReturn the reference draws as an unparsed JSON string.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.model-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase, String}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.model","text":"model(db::PosteriorDatabase, name::String) -> Model\n\nReturn a model object for the model with name name in the database db.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.model-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Posterior}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.model","text":"model(posterior::Posterior) -> Model\n\nReturn the model entry of posterior.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.model_names-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.model_names","text":"model_names(db::PosteriorDatabase) -> Vector{String}\n\nReturn the names of all models in the database.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.name-Tuple{Any}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.name","text":"name(obj) -> String\n\nReturn the name of obj.\n\nobj can be a Posterior, Model, Dataset, or ReferencePosterior.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.path-Tuple{PosteriorDB.AbstractImplementation}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.path","text":"path(implementation::AbstractImplementation) -> String\n\nAbsolute path to the file containing the model implementation.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.path-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Dataset}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.path","text":"path(dataset::Dataset) -> String\n\nAbsolute path to the file containing the model dataset.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.path-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.path","text":"path(db::PosteriorDatabase) -> String\n\nAbsolute path to the database db.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.path-Tuple{PosteriorDB.ReferencePosterior}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.path","text":"path(rp::ReferencePosterior) -> String\n\nReturn the path to the file storing the reference draws for the reference posterior rp.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.posterior-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase, String}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.posterior","text":"posterior(db::PosteriorDatabase, name::String) -> Posterior\n\nReturn a posterior object for the posterior with name name in the database db.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.posterior_names-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.posterior_names","text":"posterior_names(db::PosteriorDatabase) -> Vector{String}\n\nReturn the names of all posteriors in the database.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.recursive_stack-Tuple{Any, Any}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.recursive_stack","text":"recursive_stack(x::AbstractArray)\n\nIf x is an array of arrays, recursively stack into a single array whose dimensions are ordered with dimensions of the innermost container first and outermost last.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.reference_posterior-Tuple{PosteriorDB.PosteriorDatabase, String}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.reference_posterior","text":"reference_posterior(db::PosteriorDatabase, name::String) -> ReferencePosterior\n\nReturn a pointer to the reference posterior with name name in the database db.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"api/#PosteriorDB.reference_posterior-Tuple{PosteriorDB.Posterior}","page":"API","title":"PosteriorDB.reference_posterior","text":"reference_posterior(posterior::Posterior) -> Union{Nothing,ReferencePosterior}\n\nReturn the reference posterior entry of posterior.\n\nIf no reference posterior is available, nothing is returned.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#PosteriorDB.jl","page":"Home","title":"PosteriorDB.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.jl is a Julia package for easily working with a posteriordb database. It includes convenience functions for accessing data, model code, and information for individual posteriors, models, data, and reference draws.","category":"page"},{"location":"#Installation","page":"Home","title":"Installation","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB can be installed from the Julia general registry with","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"] add PosteriorDB","category":"page"},{"location":"#Example-usage","page":"Home","title":"Example usage","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"When PosteriorDB.jl is installed, a copy of posteriordb is downloaded. When a database is created with database, this is automatically used.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"using PosteriorDB\npdb = PosteriorDB.database()\nPosteriorDB.path(pdb)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"For now, the database is read-only. We can list the available posteriors with posterior_names.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.posterior_names(pdb)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"We can also list available models with model_names and datasets with dataset_names.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.model_names(pdb)\nPosteriorDB.dataset_names(pdb)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"We can fetch a posterior using its name and posterior.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"post = PosteriorDB.posterior(pdb, \"eight_schools-eight_schools_centered\")","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Each posterior has a corresponding model and dataset, which can be fetched with model and dataset.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"mod = PosteriorDB.model(post)\ndata = PosteriorDB.dataset(post)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"The same model and dataset can be accessed directly from the database.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.model(pdb, \"eight_schools_centered\")\nPosteriorDB.dataset(pdb, \"eight_schools\")","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"The functions database, name, and info can be applied to any posterior, model, or dataset.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.database(post)\nPosteriorDB.name(post)\nPosteriorDB.info(post)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"From the model we can access implementation code and model information.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"impl = PosteriorDB.implementation(mod, \"stan\")\nPosteriorDB.path(impl)\nmod_code = PosteriorDB.load(impl)\nprintln(mod_code)\nPosteriorDB.info(mod)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"We can access information about the dataset and load it with load.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"PosteriorDB.info(data)\nPosteriorDB.path(data)\nPosteriorDB.load(data)\nPosteriorDB.load(data, String)","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Lastly, we can access gold standard posterior draws with reference_posterior and load.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"ref = PosteriorDB.reference_posterior(post)\nPosteriorDB.info(ref)\nPosteriorDB.path(ref)\nusing DataFrames\nDataFrame(PosteriorDB.load(ref))\nPosteriorDB.load(ref, String)","category":"page"},{"location":"#Citing-PosteriorDB.jl","page":"Home","title":"Citing PosteriorDB.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"If you use PosteriorDB.jl, please cite it using the metadata in the CITATION.cff file. Please also consider citing the posteriordb software and paper whose metadata are also included. To generate a citation file in an arbitrary format, click \"Cite this repository\" on the right on the repo homepage.","category":"page"}]
